With several projects the custom fields listing page gets complicated. 

A simple filter by Project/Issue Type could be very useful.

When on the "Manage Filters" tab and the current filter is changed, a warning message is displayed:

{quote}
Filter modified since loading - click View & Hide for filter operations
{quote}

This message should only be displayed if the user is in the edit view where they must select that button to see the save operation.

